  "description": {
    "zh": "不能说我们已经到终点了，但确实越来越近了。解密需要额外的电子设备。硬件很容易坏，这很正常。我需要CPU、内存条和一块显卡。\n\n时间方面，没有这些组件，解密大约需要一天。有了它们，几乎是瞬间完成。",
    "en": "Wouldn't say we're at the finish line, but we're definitely getting close. We need additional electronics for the decryption. Hardware fails quickly, it's pretty common. I need CPUs, RAM sticks, and a graphics card.\n\nTime-wise, without these components, the decryption will take about a day. With them, it's almost instantaneous."
